Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libpcl-dev, ros-humble-laser-geometry, ros-humble-launch, ros-humble-launch-ros, ros-humble-message-filters, ros-humble-pcl-conversions, ros-humble-rclcpp, ros-humble-rclcpp-components, ros-humble-sensor-msgs, ros-humble-tf2, ros-humble-tf2-ros, ros-humble-tf2-sensor-msgs, ros-humble-visualization-msgs
Description: Converts a 3D Point Cloud into a 2D laser scan.
 This is useful for making devices like the Kinect appear like a laser scanner for 2D-based algorithms (e.g. laser-based SLAM).
